      *                          * Se l'impostazione non e' necessaria *
      *                          * e i valori da visualizzare sono dal *
      *                          * chiamante o dalla fase gestionale   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Flag di No impostazione : a     *
      *                              * seconda se parametri modifica-  *
      *                              * bili                            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-pms-snx-mod        =    "S"
                     move  "S"            to   w-cnt-acc-prm-amc
           else      move  "N"            to   w-cnt-acc-prm-amc      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Valori da visualizzare          *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Ampiezza caratteri          *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           if        r-fix-amp-car        not  = zero
                     move  r-fix-amp-car  to   w-acc-amp-car
           else      move  w-pms-amp-car  to   w-acc-amp-car          .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Ad editing ampiezza carat-  *
      *                                  * teri                        *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-079.
       cnt-acc-prm-072.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se l'impostazione e' necessaria     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Flag di Si impostazione         *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-acc-prm-amc      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Test se e' prevista una ampiez- *
      *                              * za caratteri di default asso-   *
      *                              * ciata all'utente                *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-ute-amc-def        not  = zero
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-074.
       cnt-acc-prm-073.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se non e' prevista una ampiezza *
      *                              * caratteri di default associata  *
      *                              * all'utente                      *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Ampiezza caratteri          *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-acc-amp-car          .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Ad editing ampiezza carat-  *
      *                                  * teri                        *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-079.
       cnt-acc-prm-074.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se e' prevista una ampiezza ca- *
      *                              * ratteri di default associata    *
      *                              * all'utente                      *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Ampiezza caratteri di de-   *
      *                                  * fault provvisoriamente pari *
      *                                  * all'ampiezza caratteri as-  *
      *                                  * sociata al terminale        *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-ute-amc-def        to   w-acc-amp-car          .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Test se e' possibile l'ese- *
      *                                  * cuzione del controllo sulla *
      *                                  * ampiezza caratteri in rap-  *
      *                                  * porto al codice modulo, al  *
      *                                  * codice stampante, e all'am- *
      *                                  * piezza della linea di stam- *
      *                                  * pa, ovvero se la linea puo' *
      *                                  * essere contenuta nel modulo *
      *                                  * tenendo conto del margine   *
      *                                  * perso per la stampante sia  *
      *                                  * a sinistra che a destra     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Se codice stampante non *
      *                                      * pronto : controllo non  *
      *                                      * possibile, ad editing   *
      *                                      * ampiezza caratteri      *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           if        r-fix-cod-stp        =    spaces and
                     w-pms-cod-stp        =    spaces and
                     w-acc-cod-stp        =    spaces
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-079.
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Se codice modulo non    *
      *                                      * pronto : controllo non  *
      *                                      * possibile, ad editing   *
      *                                      * ampiezza caratteri      *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           if        r-fix-cod-mod        =    spaces and
                     w-pms-cod-mod        =    spaces and
                     w-acc-cod-mod        =    spaces
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-079.
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Esecuzione controllo    *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      w-acc-amp-car        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-amc      .
           move      r-fix-amp-lin        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-als      .
           move      w-tst-cla-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-clt      .
           move      w-tst-scl-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-sct      .
           move      w-mod-tip-mod        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-tmo      .
           move      w-mod-l72-mod        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-mla      .
           move      w-tst-msi-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-ssi      .
           move      w-tst-mde-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-sde      .
           perform   cnt-amc-sml-000      thru cnt-amc-sml-999        .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Se non ci sono errori : *
      *                                      * ad editing ampiezza ca- *
      *                                      * ratteri                 *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-amc-sml-sts    =    e-not-err
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-079.
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Se ci sono errori : si  *
      *                                      * cerca tra tutte le am-  *
      *                                      * piezze caratteri sup-   *
      *                                      * portate dalla stampante *
      *                                      * quella che piu' grande  *
      *                                      * che possa essere appli- *
      *                                      * cata al modulo e che    *
      *                                      * possa essere contenuta  *
      *                                      * nell'ampiezza della li- *
      *                                      * nea di stampa. Se non   *
      *                                      * si puo' : no default    *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
       cnt-acc-prm-075.
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-acc-prm-wac      .
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-acc-prm-wi1      .
       cnt-acc-prm-076.
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-acc-prm-wi1      .
           if        w-cnt-acc-prm-wi1    >    20
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-078.
           if        w-tst-spa-ori
                    (w-cnt-acc-prm-wi1)   =    zero
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-076.
           if        w-cnt-acc-prm-wac    =    zero
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-077.
           if        w-tst-spa-ori
                    (w-cnt-acc-prm-wi1)   not  < w-cnt-acc-prm-wac
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-076.
       cnt-acc-prm-077.
           move      w-tst-spa-ori
                    (w-cnt-acc-prm-wi1)   to   w-cnt-amc-sml-amc      .
           move      r-fix-amp-lin        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-als      .
           move      w-tst-cla-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-clt      .
           move      w-tst-scl-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-sct      .
           move      w-mod-tip-mod        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-tmo      .
           move      w-mod-l72-mod        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-mla      .
           move      w-tst-msi-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-ssi      .
           move      w-tst-mde-tst        to   w-cnt-amc-sml-sde      .
           perform   cnt-amc-sml-000      thru cnt-amc-sml-999        .
           if        w-cnt-amc-sml-sts    =    e-not-err
                     move  w-tst-spa-ori
                          (w-cnt-acc-prm-wi1)
                                          to   w-cnt-acc-prm-wac      .
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-076.
       cnt-acc-prm-078.
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Se non trovata : nessun *
      *                                      * default                 *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-acc-prm-wac    =    zero
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-073.
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Se trovata : default    *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-acc-prm-wac    to   w-acc-amp-car          .
       cnt-acc-prm-079.
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Editing ampiezza carat- *
      *                                      * teri                    *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      02                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<BD"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-acc-amp-car        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-acc-amp-edt          .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Proseguimento           *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-080.
       cnt-acc-prm-080.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Altezza interlinea - inibita (07/09/04)     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Forzatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        r-fix-alt-int        not  = zero
                     move  r-fix-alt-int  to   w-acc-alt-int
           else      move  06,00          to   w-acc-alt-int          .
       cnt-acc-prm-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Save video                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   sav-imm-vid-000      thru sav-imm-vid-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione preliminare                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Video in Off                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Box vuoto                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      04                   to   v-pos                  .
           add       w-dsp-cnt-acc-prm    to   v-pos                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      77                   to   v-pto                  .
           add       w-dsp-cnt-acc-prm    to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Informazioni interne al box                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Titolo                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      37                   to   v-car                  .
           move      06                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      22                   to   v-pos                  .
           add       w-dsp-cnt-acc-prm    to   v-pos                  .
           move      "  SELEZIONE PARAMETRI PER LA STAMPA  "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura titolo                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      70                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           add       w-dsp-cnt-acc-prm    to   v-pos                  .
           move      all "-"              to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice stampante                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Literal                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-stp-000      thru pmt-cod-stp-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Valore                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cod-stp-000      thru vis-cod-stp-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Descrizione stampante               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cod-stp-des-000  thru vis-cod-stp-des-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice modulo                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Literal                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-mod-000      thru pmt-cod-mod-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Valore                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cod-mod-000      thru vis-cod-mod-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Descrizione modulo                  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cod-mod-des-000  thru vis-cod-mod-des-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo di stampa                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Literal                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tip-sta-000      thru pmt-tip-sta-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Valore                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tip-sta-000      thru vis-tip-sta-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ampiezza caratteri                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Literal                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-amp-car-000      thru pmt-amp-car-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test sul tipo stampante             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        r-fix-amp-car        not  = zero or
                     w-pms-amp-car        not  = zero
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-180.
           if        w-tst-cla-tst        =    "PS  " or
                     w-tst-cla-tst        =    "PCL5" or
                     w-tst-cla-tst        =    "SPPX" or
                     w-tst-cla-tst        =    "FAX "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-180.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Valore                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      27                   to   v-pos                  .
           add       w-dsp-cnt-acc-prm    to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-acc-amp-edt        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Altezza interlinea - Inibita (07/09/04) *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
       cnt-acc-prm-180.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Video in On                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       cnt-acc-prm-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione parametri                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione func-key di impostazione    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
       cnt-acc-prm-225.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice stampante                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cod-stp-000      thru acc-cod-stp-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-prm-sts    not  = e-not-err
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-200.
       cnt-acc-prm-250.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice modulo                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cod-mod-000      thru acc-cod-mod-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-225.
       cnt-acc-prm-275.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo di stampa                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tip-sta-000      thru acc-tip-sta-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-250.
       cnt-acc-prm-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Nome file                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-nom-fil-000      thru acc-nom-fil-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-275.
       cnt-acc-prm-325.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero di fax                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-num-fax-000      thru acc-num-fax-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-300.
       cnt-acc-prm-350.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ora di invio                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-snd-tim-000      thru acc-snd-tim-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-325.
       cnt-acc-prm-375.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Destinatario fax                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-dst-fax-000      thru acc-dst-fax-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-350.
       cnt-acc-prm-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Indirizzo e-mail                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-ind-ema-000      thru acc-ind-ema-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-375.
       cnt-acc-prm-425.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Oggetto e-mail                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-ogg-ema-000      thru acc-ogg-ema-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-400.
       cnt-acc-prm-550.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ampiezza caratteri                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-amp-car-000      thru acc-amp-car-999        .
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-700.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-425.
       cnt-acc-prm-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Conferma impostazioni                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiesta di conferma                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cnf-imp-000      thru acc-cnf-imp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Exit : uscita                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Up : reimpostazioni                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-200.
       cnt-acc-prm-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo su impegno stampante e modulo montato *
      *              * con possibilita' di montaggio del modulo estem- *
      *              * poraneamente                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Esecuzione controllo                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cnt-ist-mmo-000      thru cnt-ist-mmo-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su esito controllo                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-ist-mmo-sts    =    e-not-err
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-725
           else if   w-cnt-ist-mmo-sts    =    "20"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-750
           else if   w-cnt-ist-mmo-sts    =    "90"
                     go to cnt-acc-prm-775
           else      go to cnt-acc-prm-800.
       cnt-acc-prm-725.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se impegno stampante riuscito               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-900.
       cnt-acc-prm-750.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se impegno stampante non riuscito           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Rientro a conferma impostazioni         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-600.
       cnt-acc-prm-775.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se rinuncia all'esecuzione della stampa     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Status di uscita a '90'                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "90"                 to   w-cnt-acc-prm-sts      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-900.
       cnt-acc-prm-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se errore di i-o in impegno stampante       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Status di uscita a '99'                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "99"                 to   w-cnt-acc-prm-sts      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-900.
       cnt-acc-prm-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Restore video                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   rip-imm-vid-000      thru rip-imm-vid-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-acc-prm-999.
       cnt-acc-prm-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt campo : Codice stampante                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-cod-stp-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      09                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           add       w-dsp-cnt-acc-prm    to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Codice stampante   :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
