      *                  * stampa in spool non consentita dal sistema  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-stp-cod-stp        to   w-box-err-300-cst      .
           move      w-stp-des-stp        to   w-box-err-300-dst      .
           perform   box-err-300-000      thru box-err-300-999        .
