           move      r-env-cod-azi        to   w-imp-azi-imp          .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Codice terminale        *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      r-env-cod-ter        to   w-imp-ter-imp          .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Codice utente           *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      r-env-cod-ute        to   w-imp-ute-imp          .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Sistema applicativo     *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      r-ide-sis-app        to   w-imp-sap-imp          .
