      *                                      * Area gestionale         *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      r-ide-are-ges        to   w-imp-arg-imp          .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Settore gestionale      *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      r-ide-set-ges        to   w-imp-set-imp          .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * Fase gestionale         *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      r-ide-fas-ges        to   w-imp-fas-imp          .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
      *                                      * System date and time    *
      *                                      *-------------------------*
           move      r-env-dat-tim        to   w-imp-sdt-imp          .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
