      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-stp-can-stp        to   w-rew-imp-pss-can      .
           perform   rew-imp-pss-000      thru rew-imp-pss-999        .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Test se errori              *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           if        w-rew-imp-pss-sts    =    e-not-err
                     go to cnt-ist-mmo-380.
