      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice utente                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      r-env-cod-ute        to   p-sel-cod-ute          .
       pre-ass-sgr-280.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
