      *                      * blaggio                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test                                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-can-stp
                    (1 : 5)               not  = "ucp *" and
                     w-stp-can-stp
                    (1 : 5)               not  = "ghs *" and
                     w-stp-can-stp
                    (1 : 5)               not  = "fax *" and
                     w-stp-can-stp
                    (1 : 5)               not  = "eml *"
                     go to pre-ass-sgr-695.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Subroutine di trattamento           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   pre-ass-sgr-ucp-000  thru pre-ass-sgr-ucp-999    .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Proseguimento                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     pre-ass-sgr-700.
       pre-ass-sgr-695.
