           move      w-tst-spa-ori (19)   to   p-sel-spo-tst (19)     .
           move      w-tst-spa-ori (20)   to   p-sel-spo-tst (20)     .
       pre-ass-sgr-880.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Spaziature verticali del tipo stampante     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tst-spa-ver (01)   to   p-sel-spv-tst (01)     .
