      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       opn-fil-pss-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione status di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-not-err            to   w-opn-fil-pss-sts      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione error-code                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-not-err            to   e-sts                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione pathname per [pss]                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "A0"                 to   o-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      "A5"                 to   o-ope                  .
           move      "fpx"                to   o-com                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      "A5"                 to   o-ope                  .
           move      "pss"                to   o-com                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      "A9"                 to   o-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      o-pat                to   f-pss-pat              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Operazione di Open                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           open      i-o    pss                                       .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errori                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        e-sts                =    e-not-err
                     go to opn-fil-pss-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Status di uscita ad errore                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      e-sts                to   w-opn-fil-pss-sts      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Emissione messaggio di errore               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      f-pss-nam            to   w-box-err-fil-nam      .
           move      f-pss-pat            to   w-box-err-fil-pat      .
           move      01                   to   w-box-err-fil-fun      .
           move      e-sts                to   w-box-err-fil-cod      .
           perform   box-err-fil-000      thru box-err-fil-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiusura forzata [pss]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cls-fil-pss-000      thru cls-fil-pss-999        .
       opn-fil-pss-999.
           exit.

